#: saebooks_web/eid_sso.py:93
msgid "You declined the sign-in request on your device."
msgstr "You declined the sign-in request on your device."

#: saebooks_web/eid_sso.py:94 saebooks_web/eid_sso.py:220
msgid "The request expired before it was confirmed. Please try again."
msgstr "The request expired before it was confirmed. Please try again."

